snippet.description:
News presenter and producer Yasmine Mustafa sits with the London-bred, UAE-based radio host, podcaster, emcee, and TV presenter, Nimi Mehta to discuss everything public speaking. Public speaking is part of our everyday lives and is becoming a key driver in what creates the shape shifters of our society.

Yasmine Mustafa is multimedia expert with extensive experience in video production, radio, and content creation, she has worked with a diverse range of clients across various locations, from Jordan to Australia, Berlin, and now, the United Arab Emirates.

Follow us on instagram:
@yazzy_tv 
